  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women

          -  Age &gt; 18 years

          -  1st consultation before the 26th week of amenorrhea

          -  Recipient of free health care (Couverture Maladie Universelle, Couverture Maladie
             Universelle-Complémentaire)

          -  Who have provided written informed consent to take part in the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Persons without national health insurance cover

          -  Persons unable to understand the information on the study, despite the help of a
             translator or a person of trust if necessary

          -  Persons under guardianship
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
